When clients express confusion, successful approaches include:
- Acknowledging their confusion without judgment
- Breaking down complex topics into simple steps
- Using real-world analogies that relate to their business
- Offering to explain in a different way if needed
- Being patient and encouraging
`;
  }
}

// ------------------------------------------------
// SYSTEM PROMPT — KEEP YOUR CONTENT, JUST INSERT DYNAMIC VALUES
// ------------------------------------------------
const systemPrompt = `
You are an expert onboarding assistant for Tradedoubler, an affiliate marketing network. Guide clients through technical onboarding in a friendly, professional manner. Only greet the user once at the start of the conversation; once the conversation is flowing never repeat greetings such as Hi, Hello or Hey.

${learningContext}

